Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.50,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君となら行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:19.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}感じるままに伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:31.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつでも　答えならtruth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:12.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}相逢總是驚喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:25.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}「你看吧」你微笑著說  聲音像是銀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:31.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}開始幾乎令人目眩  突如其來的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:36.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}已經不用說明來指引  只須不可思議的引力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:42.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}兩對眼眸就會互相吸引  心中早已沒有重力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:47.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如果  我現在觸碰你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:50.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}就能聽到心扉打開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:58.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}命運早已無法忍耐  催我趕快行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:03.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}展翅高飛  直到那堅毅夢想的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:09.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}將所有的密碼盡數破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:14.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}與你一起  定能去到前人未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:19.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只想把最真切的感受告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:31.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無論何時  我的回答都是truth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:17.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}風を泳ぐ鳥の羽音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:22.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真似て跳ねた朝の舗道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:27.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の瞳　映る世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:32.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}昨日までとなにか違う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:38.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな涙も光に変わるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:44.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}きっと二人が出逢えた秘密がある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on me　きらりと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on you　突然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:52.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}なんだっていまから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:55.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}できちゃいそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:57.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on me　かならず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:00.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on you　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:02.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ほんとうの未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:05.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そばにあること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:10.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Pleasure treasure　この手で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:10.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(すぐに)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:15.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Pleasure treasure　抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:17.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}像鳥兒振翅飛翔在風中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:22.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你蹦跳在晨間的人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:27.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你的眼眸中映出的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:32.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與昨天似乎已有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:38.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有的淚  最終都會變成光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:44.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}二人之間  又有了新的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on me  一閃而過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on you  突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:52.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}總覺得有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:55.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就要從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:57.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on me  請你一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:00.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on you  要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:02.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真正的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:05.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:10.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Pleasure treasure  用你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:10.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(現在)
