Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陛下  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香緹  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你也要參加中學生錦標賽？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我參賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來好久沒有跟香緹練習過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來過兩招？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會放給對手試探技術的福利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  只有這招應該沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  果然還是來比試一下吧  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正用了她也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:44.49,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(354,620)\be2}「對手！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先從陛下的右側攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右側…是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女香緹是誠實的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒謊什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有偶爾為之喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險  香緹好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的看不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子第一次遇到那個就躲開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉香緹  我能啟動魔導器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  請便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧抓到了節奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望真是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,646)\fs36}Sacred·Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(746,646)\fs36}Contact Mode
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖之心    常態模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Set Up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了嗎  有發生什麼變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了看不到的變化  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  那就不客氣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Accel Smash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅疾破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該看不到的  卻做出了迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  這孩子居然赤手空拳就全力打上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  來互攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦  全力來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陛下的魔導器  那隻兔子的功勞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重視防禦的輔助控制型魔導器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將性能全部集中於支持防禦上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說  就是如同全身加上護具一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能面對利刃也全力打過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這溫柔的孩子和陛下真是天生一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是抱歉  我有件事比較在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要通過攻擊證實一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要反擊  全力防禦試試
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙輪劍舞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是陛下  我還沒攻過來你就看穿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然進行了防禦  但還是被切到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  香緹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被知道我在欺負陛下  那對雙胞胎又要囉嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香緹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟身為護衛的我們連招呼都不打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裏對陛下動刀子  真是好大的膽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  是我邀請她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下真是宅心仁厚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這跟那是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下您還要去看望伊克斯大人對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不讓你們進行練習比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還請在合適的場所進行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪德  你說的和做的完全不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉香緹  我們再約時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  替我向伊克斯問好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒想做什麼  只是想告訴她這麼做很危險而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然約定好的霸王愛機已經完成  就算是發佈會暨交接儀式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作這件魔導器的過程太有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們兩個做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基礎模塊是琳做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾風幫我進行了AI系統的製作和調整
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後外觀是亞基特親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  可以說是正統古代貝魯卡的特種機體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想好了主旨和基礎設計
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後聯繫薇薇歐和露露查詢了一下修托拉的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們聽說克勞斯陛下有養過豹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因為雪原豹在修托拉地區是優秀的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯他們也很重視它們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  我們就以修托拉的雪原豹為主題製作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動物型？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大的話帶在身邊不方便吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不用擔心  琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特  打開看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你們三個的心聲是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說跟想像的不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸一下試試吧  愛因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼可愛的孩子  我真的可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有進行過使用者認證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意的話你來起名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證就在院子裏做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  奧利維爾好像有一對非常喜歡的豹子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是在幼豹出生之前就想好取什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯和奧利維爾最後的歲月中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一隻沒能順利誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她原本打算給那只幼豹什麼名字來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了  是兩人都非常喜歡的小說的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個體名稱登錄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(766,646)\fs36}Asteion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是…阿斯提翁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昵稱為  提奧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(586,646)\fs36}Asteion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(734,646)\fs36}Set Up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯提翁  變身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髮型是不是換了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(598,646)\fs36}Asteion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是阿斯提翁幫你調整的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來再一點點調整吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香緹為我擔心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我現在的水平  赤手空拳出場的話肯定會一敗塗地的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我喜歡格鬥戰技
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也希望通過諾威教我的強襲鬥技讓自己變強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲也一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得比現在更強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠超過今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  從今天開始特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓為每個人分頭進行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是團隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身為選手  你們也互為競爭對手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珂羅娜小姐  恕我冒昧  願為您指導
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉奧小姐由我來指導
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你就由我來教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  教練
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說愛因哈特同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在進行對練呢  去我朋友那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與你對練  我甚感榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\3a33\3c294E5F\fs18\pos(1001,247)}拔刀術天瞳流  師範代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\fs26\pos(1052,275)}米嘉婭·捨韋勒（18歲）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\3c000000\fs22\pos(930,300)}類型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\3c000000\fs22\pos(930,325)}魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\3c000000\fs22\pos(930,350)}魔導器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\3c000000\fs22\pos(930,375)}錦標賽參賽經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\1cFFFFFF\3c000000\fs22\pos(930,400)}最高戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\an3\1cFFFFFF\3a33\3c294E5F\fs22\pos(1230,300)}拔刀居合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\an3\1cFFFFFF\3a33\3c294E5F\fs22\pos(1230,325)}近代貝魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\an3\1cFFFFFF\3a33\3c294E5F\fs22\pos(1230,350)}晴嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\an3\1cFFFFFF\3a33\3c294E5F\fs22\pos(1230,375)}7次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:46.25,POS3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,0)\an3\1cFFFFFF\3a33\3c294E5F\fs22\pos(1230,400)}城市正賽  第3名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也是參賽選手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不會放水太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為體會斬擊的危險性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我則為應對你這種近戰型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們互惠互利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是  我會盡全力為您效勞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了薇薇歐  我們這就開始特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你說說你的缺點是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦太脆弱  攻擊的力度也不夠大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整體力量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那優點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我不是跟你說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的優點首先就是你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視野寬闊  把握距離也很精確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有足以活用這雙眼的快速反應和動作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後是你敢於向前的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最能發揮這些長處的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防守反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是諾威教我的打法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  你今後也要保持這種打法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼珂羅娜小姐  讓我們開始特訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(658,646)\fs36}Golem Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將針對魔像創主的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻礙創成並且緊盯創主進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉奧小姐那技術體系中包含武器戰鬥的春光拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該如何防禦我的光劍雙刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊的情況就這樣  好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被教訓得很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你的對手有那麼強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是實戰的話光今天我就已經死了二十次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提奧  不准爬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  愛因哈特同學  怎麼你那邊一直傳來貓的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問陸戰指導的錄像？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我倒是有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說「想知道自己能做什麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想找到方法  比現在更好地保護她」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我給你找些有用的錄像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始地區預選賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你們也都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於是個人戰  所以團隊成員之間也有可能會碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點你們都有心理準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下面發表你們四人的賽區
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉奧  預賽5組
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇歐  預賽4組
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,646)\fs36}Buster Head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在莉奧小姐的5組裏有炮擊老大哈利·翠貝卡選手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒她就無法進軍正賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會打倒她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在薇薇歐的4組裏  精英種子選手是米嘉婭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米嘉婭小姐  對練的時候受過她不少照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要一起競爭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要贏她可是非常困難的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得多加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛因哈特和珂羅娜都在1組
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便對手是愛因哈特同學  我也會努力取勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中島隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加  油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全都是參賽選手對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考核賽也總算要開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是薩菲拉  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正好  我還沒給你們好好介紹過繆拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是薇薇歐小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我是繆拉·苪那爾蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  久仰大名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想跟您見上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為薇薇歐小姐算是我的師姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢當不敢當  而且繆拉小姐比我年長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩菲拉也不過教過我一小會兒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這兔子真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫克莉絲  是我的愛機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  克莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我家那個也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過繆拉興致還真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}那個  我能摸一下它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆拉也是第一次參加大規模的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢  你們那邊情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等比賽開始就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是訓練下了不少功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  訓練很到位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強哦  我家那些小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標號  367號  554號選手  請前往C擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫到我了  開始緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆拉小姐沒問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一組  1066號  1084號選手  請前往E擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考核賽不能用魔導器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲就在這為我加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太興奮了  冷靜比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要失手傷了她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了快冷靜下來  直視你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近到有效範圍里斬殺  接近到有效範圍里斬殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近到有效範圍里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對手看起來好強  可以使出全力對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試一下新步法好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近到有效範圍里…斬殺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我練習的至始至終都對打的打法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(879,646)\fs36}Jet Step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此練成的高速追擊步法  疾捷蹴步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼近對手  以鐵拳攻之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到這地步也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見時就是賽場了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繆拉是哪組啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說過嗎  4組
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在預賽跟薇薇歐碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs44}成功了
